    {
      "start": 0.6,
      "end": 21.95,
      "text": "To enjoy a movie, screen english time"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.95,
      "end": 23.79,
      "text": "이달에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.79,
      "end": 26.05,
      "text": "Bart Frundich 감독,"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.29,
      "end": 29.11,
      "text": "Julian Moore, Michelle Williams 주연의"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.11,
      "end": 31.17,
      "text": "After the Wedding!"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.65,
      "end": 34.07,
      "text": "After the Wedding in New York!"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.31,
      "end": 34.83,
      "text": "였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.99,
      "end": 35.25,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.45,
      "end": 35.97,
      "text": "Yes!"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.23,
      "end": 37.79,
      "text": "와, 시작부터 이정자님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.59,
      "end": 40.91,
      "text": "Chris Sam, I love you!"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.15,
      "end": 42.15,
      "text": "Oh, I love you!"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.15,
      "end": 43.15,
      "text": "고백을 해주셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.15,
      "end": 44.15,
      "text": "고백까지!"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.15,
      "end": 46.15,
      "text": "아, 참 부럽습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 46.15,
      "end": 49.15,
      "text": "That is quite something special to hear in the morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.15,
      "end": 52.15,
      "text": "Yeah, 아주 big fans 분들이 참 많이 계십니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.15,
      "end": 53.15,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.15,
      "end": 54.15,
      "text": "It's hard to say that in the morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 54.15,
      "end": 55.15,
      "text": "To your own family!"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.15,
      "end": 56.15,
      "text": "Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.15,
      "end": 57.15,
      "text": "Oh, so early!"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.15,
      "end": 60.15,
      "text": "이 아침부터 마음이 몽글몽글해지네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.15,
      "end": 61.31,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.81,
      "end": 64.57,
      "text": "아무튼 최근에 제가"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.57,
      "end": 67.47,
      "text": "이 After the Wedding 영화에 관련되어서"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.47,
      "end": 70.55,
      "text": "감독하고 또 배우들 몇 명이 나온"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.55,
      "end": 72.07,
      "text": "인터뷰 영상을 봤는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.07,
      "end": 73.21,
      "text": "거기에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.21,
      "end": 78.27,
      "text": "The Director and Julian Moore have a special relationship."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.57,
      "end": 79.85,
      "text": "Yeah, I didn't know this."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.21,
      "end": 82.51,
      "text": "They have a very special relationship."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.73,
      "end": 85.23,
      "text": "저도 이 인터뷰를 보기 전까지는"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.23,
      "end": 86.43,
      "text": "잘 몰랐어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.59,
      "end": 89.03,
      "text": "근데 아주 특별한 관계였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.03,
      "end": 92.03,
      "text": "Did you see the interview with both of them together?"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.03,
      "end": 92.53,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.53,
      "end": 93.53,
      "text": "Yeah, together."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.53,
      "end": 94.03,
      "text": "Yeah?"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.03,
      "end": 96.03,
      "text": "Don't they look good together?"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.03,
      "end": 99.03,
      "text": "아주 lovely한 그런 chemistry가 느껴졌어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.03,
      "end": 100.03,
      "text": "Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.03,
      "end": 101.03,
      "text": "전생연분?"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.03,
      "end": 103.03,
      "text": "They look like a match made in heaven."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.03,
      "end": 104.03,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.03,
      "end": 105.03,
      "text": "They look like they're in love."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.03,
      "end": 106.03,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.03,
      "end": 108.03,
      "text": "과연 어떤 사이일까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.03,
      "end": 111.03,
      "text": "지금 약간 갸우뚱갸우뚱하고 계실 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.03,
      "end": 113.03,
      "text": "아마 감 잡으신 분들도 많이 계실 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.03,
      "end": 114.03,
      "text": "Not a boyfriend and girlfriend."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.03,
      "end": 115.03,
      "text": "They're not dating."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.03,
      "end": 118.03,
      "text": "They are actually, yes, they're married."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.03,
      "end": 119.03,
      "text": "Yeah, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.03,
      "end": 120.03,
      "text": "Bart Fröndlick."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.03,
      "end": 123.03,
      "text": "I think he's of German ancestry."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.03,
      "end": 125.03,
      "text": "That's a German name, I think."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.03,
      "end": 126.03,
      "text": "Fröndlick."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.03,
      "end": 127.03,
      "text": "Ah, Fröndlick."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.03,
      "end": 131.03,
      "text": "독일 출신이 아닌가 싶다라는 말씀을 해주셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.03,
      "end": 132.03,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.03,
      "end": 137.03,
      "text": "So he met Miss Julianne Moore on a movie set."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.03,
      "end": 143.03,
      "text": "He was the director and producer of a movie called The Myth of Fingerprints back in 1997."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.03,
      "end": 144.03,
      "text": "And that's where he met Julianne Moore."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.03,
      "end": 146.03,
      "text": "And that's where he met Julianne Moore."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.03,
      "end": 148.03,
      "text": "And they've been married since 2003."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.03,
      "end": 149.03,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.03,
      "end": 150.03,
      "text": "So that's a long time."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.03,
      "end": 151.03,
      "text": "So that's a long time."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.03,
      "end": 152.03,
      "text": "Almost 23, 20 years."
    },
    {
      "start": 152.03,
      "end": 153.03,
      "text": "20 years."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.03,
      "end": 154.03,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.03,
      "end": 155.03,
      "text": "More than 20 years."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.03,
      "end": 156.03,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.03,
      "end": 160.03,
      "text": "지금 결혼을 한 지 한 20주년 이상 된 관계입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.03,
      "end": 161.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.03,
      "end": 162.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.03,
      "end": 163.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.03,
      "end": 165.03,
      "text": "They were talking about their secret for marriage."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.03,
      "end": 166.03,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.03,
      "end": 167.03,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.03,
      "end": 168.03,
      "text": "Very interesting."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.03,
      "end": 175.03,
      "text": "And they said, they both, or Julianne said, both sides, the man and the woman, want to be married."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.03,
      "end": 176.03,
      "text": "Whoa."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.03,
      "end": 181.03,
      "text": "Oftentimes, you know, after marriage, one side doesn't really want to be married."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.03,
      "end": 182.03,
      "text": "Ah."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.03,
      "end": 186.03,
      "text": "But yeah, she said, they both want to be married and he needs to make me laugh."
    },
    {
      "start": 186.03,
      "end": 187.03,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.03,
      "end": 188.03,
      "text": "He needs to make me laugh."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.03,
      "end": 190.03,
      "text": "Otherwise, it's really, really difficult."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.03,
      "end": 191.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.03,
      "end": 192.03,
      "text": "Those, you know, everyday life."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.03,
      "end": 193.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.03,
      "end": 197.03,
      "text": "Everyday chores are very difficult if you don't smile, you don't laugh."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.03,
      "end": 198.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.03,
      "end": 205.03,
      "text": "매일매일 웃게 해주려고 노력하는 상대가 있다는 게 참 특별하고 좋은 거 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 205.03,
      "end": 206.03,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.03,
      "end": 207.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.03,
      "end": 210.03,
      "text": "So, actually, he approached her first on the movie set."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.03,
      "end": 211.03,
      "text": "Aha."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.03,
      "end": 213.03,
      "text": "He came up to her and she looked a little cold."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.03,
      "end": 214.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.03,
      "end": 217.03,
      "text": "So, he thought about putting his arm around her."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.03,
      "end": 218.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.03,
      "end": 219.03,
      "text": "But, no."
    },
    {
      "start": 219.03,
      "end": 220.03,
      "text": "That's too much."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.03,
      "end": 221.03,
      "text": "He didn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 221.03,
      "end": 224.03,
      "text": "He didn't want to smother her freedom of expression."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.03,
      "end": 225.03,
      "text": "She's a free soul."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.03,
      "end": 226.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.03,
      "end": 228.03,
      "text": "And her acting is very individualistic."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.03,
      "end": 229.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.03,
      "end": 231.03,
      "text": "He felt like he should not control her too much."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.03,
      "end": 232.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.03,
      "end": 233.03,
      "text": "So, he gave her her space."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.03,
      "end": 234.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 234.03,
      "end": 236.03,
      "text": "But, he really respected her as an artist."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.03,
      "end": 237.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.03,
      "end": 238.03,
      "text": "And, he liked her as a person."
    },
    {
      "start": 238.03,
      "end": 239.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.03,
      "end": 241.03,
      "text": "And, things, they hit things off."
    },
    {
      "start": 241.03,
      "end": 242.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.03,
      "end": 243.03,
      "text": "And, yeah, the rest is history."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.03,
      "end": 244.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.03,
      "end": 245.03,
      "text": "They got married."
    },
    {
      "start": 245.03,
      "end": 246.03,
      "text": "Eventually."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.03,
      "end": 252.03,
      "text": "참, 처음에 어떻게 이 둘이 가까워지게 됐는지 살짝만 들어봤는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.03,
      "end": 256.03,
      "text": "확실히 이 줄리안 모어가 약간 추워보였을 때,"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.03,
      "end": 258.03,
      "text": "그때가 시작점이 된 게 아닌가 싶어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.03,
      "end": 260.03,
      "text": "그러니까, she started up his protective instinct."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.03,
      "end": 261.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.03,
      "end": 263.03,
      "text": "Oh, I don't want her to be cold."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.03,
      "end": 266.03,
      "text": "But, if I put my arm around her, or give her a jacket,"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.03,
      "end": 267.03,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 267.03,
      "end": 268.03,
      "text": "It's too much."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.03,
      "end": 269.03,
      "text": "It'll seem like I'm trying to control her."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.03,
      "end": 270.03,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.03,
      "end": 272.03,
      "text": "As a director, I want to give her freedom."
    },
    {
      "start": 272.03,
      "end": 273.03,
      "text": "But, I also like her."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.03,
      "end": 274.03,
      "text": "What should I do?"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.03,
      "end": 279.03,
      "text": "자, 이렇게 존중을 하는 마음과 함께 배려심까지 잘 혼합이 되어가지고,"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.03,
      "end": 281.03,
      "text": "여전히 they still look like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.03,
      "end": 283.03,
      "text": "사이가 아주 좋아 보입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 283.03,
      "end": 284.03,
      "text": "Genuinely."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.03,
      "end": 288.03,
      "text": "Yeah, there's not many couples that I've seen who've been married over 20 years"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.03,
      "end": 290.03,
      "text": "that look like that much in love."
    },
    {
      "start": 290.03,
      "end": 291.03,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.03,
      "end": 293.03,
      "text": "눈에서 꼴이 뚝뚝 떨어졌어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.03,
      "end": 294.03,
      "text": "정말 떨어졌어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.03,
      "end": 297.03,
      "text": "네, 비법이 뭔지 점점 더 알고 싶네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.03,
      "end": 298.03,
      "text": "Anyway, I respect them."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.03,
      "end": 299.03,
      "text": "Yep."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.03,
      "end": 300.03,
      "text": "Me too."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.03,
      "end": 301.03,
      "text": "Let's do that."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.03,
      "end": 302.03,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.03,
      "end": 304.03,
      "text": "오늘 장면 먼저 확인하고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.03,
      "end": 305.03,
      "text": "Mom."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.03,
      "end": 308.03,
      "text": "You've made this night so special."
    },
    {
      "start": 308.03,
      "end": 318.29,
      "text": "You are the most caring, loving, best example of a woman I could have ever asked for in a mother."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.29,
      "end": 326.47,
      "text": "And for those of you who don't know, I had the rare experience of getting to choose my own mother."
    },
    {
      "start": 326.47,
      "end": 330.72,
      "text": "It was just me and my dad for the first year of my life."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.72,
      "end": 335.72,
      "text": "네, 지금 누구의 목소리냐면 바로 Grace라는 사람의 목소리인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.72,
      "end": 336.72,
      "text": "The daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.72,
      "end": 338.72,
      "text": "Yeah, of Teresa, 그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.72,
      "end": 340.72,
      "text": "And this is where the drama begins."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.72,
      "end": 341.72,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.72,
      "end": 343.72,
      "text": "The juicy drama."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.72,
      "end": 346.72,
      "text": "Juicy drama가 시작이 되는 시점입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.72,
      "end": 353.72,
      "text": "지금 이 그레이스가 on her wedding에서 지금 she's expressing her gratitude to her parents."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.72,
      "end": 358.72,
      "text": "Yeah, you know, in American weddings, they have big dinners and they usually give a toast."
    },
    {
      "start": 358.72,
      "end": 359.72,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
